{"type":"message","id":"b9e9cdd4","parentId":"0ab39213","timestamp":"2026-02-08T12:25:42.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很有趣的发现！通过代理和不通过代理的结果不同：\n- 不使用代理：命令执行失败（可能是网络问题）\n- 使用 SOCKS5 代理 (20170)：返回 IP 62.192.175.118\n- 使用 HTTP 代理 (20171)：返回 IP 62.192.175.95\n\n这两个 IP 不同，说明代理确实在工作，而且两个端口可能转发到不同的节点。\n\n但问题可能在于用户提到的\"代理端口测试失败（curl 返回 000）\"。让我再仔细检查一下当前的状态。\n\n实际上，从测试来看代理是工作的。用户可能：\n1. 在测试时没有选中任何节点\n2. 节点本身有问题\n3. 或者测试命令有问题\n\n让我查看一下是否有任何节点被选中或者是否有特定的节点在运行。","thinkingSignature":"9534616cc82cf9349faf73f2ecc504fd4401c6a90e5c42f5f1d21a300b4d0b7a"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我明白了！让我查看 v2rayA 的实际运行状态和配置：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_skjih44izra1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://127.0.0.1:2017/api/v1/status 2>&1","security":"deny"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_skjih44izra1_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps aux | grep -E '[v2]ray' | grep -v grep","security":"deny"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.1","usage":{"input":48078,"output":282,"cacheRead":10081,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58441,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770553522107}}
